of the faculty.

161
00:07:57,028 --> 00:07:59,895
Naw, he's gonna
stroke to 'em later.

162
00:08:02,933 --> 00:08:04,969
Why don't you let
Loretta do that?

163
00:08:05,004 --> 00:08:08,271
She can handle the homework.
I'll handle the silver.

164
00:08:08,305 --> 00:08:11,209
What'd you land on?

165
00:08:11,244 --> 00:08:14,876
Rumaki, Crab Louie
on toast points,

166
00:08:14,911 --> 00:08:16,979
and little franks
in barbecue sauce.

167
00:08:17,015 --> 00:08:19,584
You know they've got four more
houses to visit after us?

168
00:08:19,618 --> 00:08:22,319
