to put everyone at ease.

169
00:08:22,353 --> 00:08:24,153
They get so
tongue-tied around us.

170
00:08:24,188 --> 00:08:27,259
They can only pretend so long
we're just "regular neighbors."

171
00:08:29,629 --> 00:08:31,397
Could you stock the bar?

172
00:08:31,431 --> 00:08:34,699
