Grilled cheese? Spaghetti?

197
00:09:42,543 --> 00:09:46,113
Do you have any meat?
I've been dreaming about it.

198
00:09:46,148 --> 00:09:48,051
( laughs )
Sure.

199
00:09:48,085 --> 00:09:50,619
Now you go into the bedroom
back there.

200
00:09:50,653 --> 00:09:52,588
I changed the sheets.
There are towels.

201
00:09:52,622 --> 00:09:54,687
You can lie down, run a bath,

202
00:09:54,722 --> 00:09:57,490
whatever you want.
Make yourself at home.

203
00:09:57,524 --> 00:09:59,959
Thank you.
I'm pretty beat.

204
00:10:11,541 --> 00:10:13,375
You know I want her.

205
