210
00:10:51,980 --> 00:10:54,516
Don, why don't you take the
mound, throw out the first pitch?

211
00:10:54,550 --> 00:10:56,315
Sure.

212
00:10:56,349 --> 00:11:00,354
Stan has some
very preliminary work.

213
00:11:00,388 --> 00:11:02,422
Stan?

214
00:11:02,456 --> 00:11:05,592
Should I move over there or do
you want to come over here?

215
00:11:05,626 --> 00:11:07,894
I don't know, Stan. Can you
be smug from over there?

216
00:11:09,997 --> 00:11:11,464
Lou, I don't know
what you think you heard.

217
00:11:11,498 --> 00:11:13,266
